\begin_layout Standard

\change_inserted 78966105 1467135568
On average, cells from these four groups had approximately 
\begin_inset Formula $\sim170,125,85$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $40$
\end_inset

 postsynaptic (inputs) sites respectively (Fig.
